title: Surprise! Felicia Day Announces Pregnancy 3 Weeks Ahead of Baby's Due Date
text: Surprise! Felicia Day Announces Pregnancy 3 Weeks Ahead of Baby's Due Date by Jennifer Drysdale 4:30 PM PST, January 03, 2017 Photo: Instagram Congratulations to Felicia Day! WATCH: Ellen Pompeo and Husband Chris Ivery Welcome Baby No. 3 Day took to Twitter on Tuesday to share the big news with her followers, alongside a totally bumpin' shot of her belly. "She's coming in about three weeks so I guess I should announce this and stuff," she captioned the pic. She's coming in about three weeks so I guess I should announce this and stuff. pic.twitter.com/OCZw2CoHvr RELATED: Lauren Conrad Pregnant With First Child While Day is several weeks away from welcoming her buddle of joy, ET confirmed that another star, Janet Jackson, g ave birth to her baby boy on Tuesday. "Janet Jackson and husband Wissam Al Mana are thrilled to welcome their new son Eissa Al Mana into the world," the singer's rep told ET in a statement. "Janet had a stress-free healthy delivery and is resting comfortably." See more in the video below. RELATED SLIDESHOW
